                     <interp inst="t18260216-138-person907" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I seized hold of this woman, and took two pots from her right hand pocket.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260216-138-person908">
                  JOHN 
                  WILD
               <interp inst="t18260216-138-person908" type="surname" value="WILD"></interp>
